item.title: Pelicant, Hope Hook, and Solana and the Sunsets Friday 2.28.25
item.author: invalid@example.com (Nathan(MNHoneypants))
item.dc:creator: Nathan(MNHoneypants)
item.content:encoded:
Hi friends. I get to play bass with Hope Hook this Friday at the Underground Music Venue. The bill is super fun, that flyer is art (nice work Sam), and it will be fun to look at Underground with fresh eyes and expectations.

Come on out for some serious sway and boogie action.

item.title: 26 BATS! presents Fairy Goblin: a drag puppet music show 2/22 @ The Southern Theater
item.author: invalid@example.com (babo26)
item.dc:creator: babo26
item.content:encoded: woop woop! Using music as a soundtrack to tell a story of trans and queer magic, t4t love, and celebrating your true self with puppets!♾ we are having amazing drag performers and artists help puppeteer a story full of whimsy while my band plays songs! $10-20 tix sliding scale

item.title: Joe Bartel / Big Big Brain! / Brian James Hoffman at Badger’s Den
item.author: invalid@example.com (JoeBartel)
item.dc:creator: JoeBartel
item.content:encoded:
Hi gang! Badger's Den is an acoustic house venue in northeast Minneapolis and tomorrow night, we're having our first show of 2025!

Come hang out, see what our comfy cozy DIY venue is all about, and enjoy some great songwriters. Brian James Hoffman is on tour from South Dakota and he's also a painter, so you might end up taking home your new favorite artwork as well.

DM me here or on Instagram for the address!
